a numerical integration formula useful in fourier analysis.wa numerical integration formula is presented whichuses unequal sampling intervals.  the intervals are equally spaced on a log scale.  such a formulationis useful in fourier analysis to improve accuracy and ease of usage.  a complete set of formulasfor numerical fourier analysis is given.cacm january, meisel, w. s..knumerical integration, fourier analysis, integration.c.ca jb february ,   : pm